
Quick Start Guide - Setup An Apache/PHP Web Server on Windows in 5 Minutes
Download XAMPP Download
Download Microsoft Visual C++ Download
Install Microsoft Visual C++
Install XAMPP
After the installation completes the XAMPP Control Panel will display
Click the box under Service next to Apache and MySQL to run them as Windows Services
Open a web browser and navigate to http://localhost
Welcome to your fully functional WAMP server in under 5 minutes
